    public class CrossWithSmallOperator
extends CrossOperator
implements org.apache.flink.api.common.operators.base.CrossOperatorBase.CrossWithSmall
    This operator represents a Cartesian-Product operation. Of the two inputs, the first is expected to be large and the second is expected to be small.
